org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi

Interface AlarmsEventsModule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ApplicationModule
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlarmsEventsModuleImpl

    public interface AlarmsEventsModule
extends ApplicationModule
    A representation of the model object 'Alarms Events Module'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Monitor Pool Proxies
    • Event Pool Proxies
    • Akn Proxies
    • Pull Events

    See Also:
    OsgiPackage.getAlarmsEventsModule()
